criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients attending the bariatric surgery's ambulatory;

          -  patients presenting body mass index (BMI) ≥ 40 kg/m2.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  acute or chronic pulmonary diseases;

          -  smoking;

          -  not stable cardiovascular diseases;

          -  decompensated diabetes.
